                        "displayName": "Kouhei Sutou",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Asia/Tokyo"
                    },
                    "body": "{{LD_LIBRARY_PATH=${CONDA_ROOT}/lib}} is needed for resolving the error.\r\nIf we don't have the {{LD_LIBRARY_PATH}}, the system {{libglib-2.0.so}} not the conda {{libglib-2.0.so}} is referred.\r\n\r\nNormally, do normal conda users set {{LD_LIBRARY_PATH}}?",
